&lt;h4&gt;ABOUT YOU&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive net-new enterprise business across a defined strategic U.S. territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead complex, multi-stakeholder sales cycles with district leadership teams.&lt;/li&gt;
