&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ready to be at the forefront of innovation in K-12 education technology? Lightspeed Systems, serving millions of students and educators with a rapidly growing product line, is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;User Acceptance Testing QA Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our dynamic team. We offer more than just a job—this is an opportunity to grow your career, be recognized for your hard work, and thrive in a supportive and collaborative office environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
