&lt;li&gt;An understanding of how teachers actually use classroom management software&amp;nbsp;during instruction, and empathy for the educator experience. Prior experience in education, edtech, or K-12 environments is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management and planning skills, with the ability to prioritize and balance multiple projects in a fast-paced, high-volume environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive knowledge and hands-on experience with defect management tools, particularly JIRA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A solid foundation in manual testing, with the ability to develop thorough test cases and identify edge cases across various platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to collaborate cross-functionally with QA, developers, product managers, and technical leads to resolve defects

