&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You’ll be part strategist, part creative, part project quarterback, part tactical executioner—and 100% focused on moving the needle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
